- 'Top-ranked portfolio' refers to the first portfolio in the ranking based on the portfolio name;
- 'Multiple analyst comments' means more than one comment;
- 'Majority of buy ratings' means over 50% of the ratings are 'Buy';
- 'Reported over a billion dollars in revenue' means total revenue is greater than 1,000,000,000.0 for the year ending March 2022.

- 'Buy' ratings are a recommendation to purchase stock in a company;
- Analysts are financial professionals who provide investment advice;
- The sector 'Consumer Goods' includes companies that produce goods for consumer use.

sql:
SELECT company_id, COUNT(comment_id) AS comment_count
FROM analyst_comments
GROUP BY company_id;

